<rgb=#686868>(This document appears to have been a poster of some kind.)</rgb>

'Beware Inkanûsh, the Secret Man! Appearing as a mad old man, always garbed in grey, who causes confusion wherever he walks.

Inkanûsh leads unwise young people into danger.
Inkanûsh causes widespread disasters and madness.
He is a trickster who can conjure flame from the air!
He is a fool who gets himself into all manner of trouble and is always saved by luck.
He is many things and goes by many names.
Avoid him always, or catastrophe will befall you!'
